  "prompt": "What is a good place to learn singing in hyderabad?",
  "response": "Hyderabad offers several reputed places where you can learn singing, whether you're a beginner or looking to refine your skills. Here are some great options:\n\n### 1. **Swar Sudha (Jubilee Hills & Kukatpally)**\n   - Known for its structured curriculum and experienced faculty.\n   - Offers training in Carnatic, Hindustani, and Western vocal music.\n   - Website: [www.swarsudha.in](http://www.swarsudha.in)\n\n### 2. **Saptaswara Music Academy (Madhapur & Banjara Hills)**\n   - Focuses on Carnatic and Western classical singing.\n   - Provides individual attention to students.\n   - Website: [www.saptaswara.in](http://www.saptaswara.in)\n\n### 3. **Furtados School of Music (Banjara Hills)**\n   - Specializes in Western and contemporary music styles.\n   - Offers personalized coaching and workshops.\n   - Website: [www.furtadosschoolofmusic.com](https://www.furtadosschoolofmusic.com)\n\n### 4. **Kala Bharti (Secunderabad & Kothapet)**\n   - Offers training in Carnatic and light music.\n   - Known for its traditional teaching methods.\n\n### 5. **Shankar Mahadevan Academy (Online & Offline)**\n   - A well-known academy with online and offline classes.\n   - Focuses on Hindustani and Bollywood-style singing.\n   - Website: [www.shankarmahadevanacademy.com](https://www.shankarmahadevanacademy.com)\n\n### 6. **Girish Music Academy (Various Locations)**\n   - Provides training in Carnatic, Hindustani, and film music.\n   - Known for its flexible timings and affordable fees.\n\n### 7. **Hyderabad Music School (Banjara Hills)**\n   - Offers courses in Western and Bollywood vocals.\n   - Ideal for beginners and advanced learners.\n\n### 8. **Little Mozart's Academy (Banjara Hills & Gachibowli)**\n   - Focuses on Western and contemporary vocal training.\n   - Provides performance opportunities for students.\n\n### 9. **Nada Brahma (Panjagutta)**\n   - Specializes in Carnatic music and offers advanced training.\n   - Known for its experienced faculty.\n\n### 10. **Harmony Music Academy (Jubilee Hills)**\n   - Offers Hindustani, Carnatic, and film music training.\n   - Provides individual and group classes.\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Right Place:\n- **Determine Your Style:** Choose a school that aligns with the genre of music you want to learn (Carnatic, Hindustani, Western, etc.).\n- **Check Faculty:** Look for experienced teachers with a good reputation.\n- **Class Size:** Smaller class sizes often mean more individual attention.\n- **Infrastructure:** Ensure the school has good facilities, such as practice rooms and audio equipment.\n- **Reviews:** Read online reviews or ask for recommendations from friends or family.\n\nWhichever place you choose, consistent practice and dedication are key to improving your singing skills!",
